Package br.com.pethub.model

Class ItemSale

java.lang.Object
br.com.pethub.model.ItemSale
public class ItemSale extends Object
This class represents an ItemSale in the application. It contains fields that represent different properties of an item sale, such as id, sale, product, qty, and subtotal. It also contains getter and setter methods for these fields.
